This paper deals with machine learning algorithms for anti-spam filtering, which involves natural language processing and classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Additionally, it deals with security and privacy (cs.CR) issues related to spam filtering. Finally, the paper uses cost-sensitive evaluation measures, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research.
